:name:
Fera II

:coretxt:
You have ability to turn into any animal you have seen.
You can turn partly or fully to any beast.
No mass is lost in transformation so this may result in giant bat or miniscule horse.

:cost:
1 Instinct

:req:
Has lived outside civilization or \SecretNameFeraA{}.

